Welcome to Moneyvesting. I'm really excited to have you on my channel. My goal is to share everything I learn about the stock markets, investing, fundamental and technical analysis. You'll find videos related to technical breakdowns on different Stocks and ETFs, Stocks and Company analysis along with Stock comparisons and market commentary on the S&P 500 and NASDAQ, market benchmarks.

I look forward to learning from you and learning about you. Please be sure to LIKE, SUBSCRIBE, and turn on NOTIFICATIONS.
Let me know in the comments if there is anything I can improve on moving forward.

DISCLAIMER
📈 Do your own due diligence (DD) and research. If you decide to buy or sell anything, that is entirely your decision and your decision alone. We want you to learn and become self-sufficient.  
📈 NEVER Trade/Invest based on other people's opinions. Please do your own analysis. Information provided on this channel is for entertainment purposes ONLY. This is NOT financial or investment advice.
